    <h1>Inflatable Screen Event Packages: What They Include and How to Choose</h1>
    <div class="blog-meta">
      <span>By Premiere Outdoor Movies</span>
      <span>·</span>
      <span>June 6, 2026</span>
    </div>
  </div>
